              La Molina
            </h3>
            <h3
              class="text-xs md:text-sm rounded p-2 font-bold mb-4 flex items-center gap-2 bg-white/10 backdrop-blur border border-white/20"
            >
              <i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt text-warm-yellow"></i>
